text.tspan: This is a regular election as defined in our Election Rules [1] so
the elected board member will serve till the end of 2022
To stand for a position in the openSUSE Board
If a member would like to nominate another
member, please inform the Election Committee
and the officials will contact the nominee to ask
whether they would like to run as a Board candidate
Only openSUSE members are eligible to run for
openSUSE Board openings in accordance with the
Eligibility and Validity section of our Election
The Election Committee [2] are hereby calling for
Nominations & Applications for the openSUSE Board
[2] Members: Ish Sookun, Edwin Zakaria and Ariez Vachha
